title: Louis Vuitton OnTheGo PM
description: Louis Vuitton OnTheGo PM bag in cream Monogram Empreinte leather (RFID response: after March, 2021). Featuring gold-toned hardware, black leather trims, rolled top handles and a detachable & adjustable shoulder strap. The hook closure opens to a cream microfiber interior with a zip pocket and 2 patch pockets. Approx dimensions: 25cm(L) x 19cm(H) x 10.5cm(D), 8.5cm handle drop & 52cm shoulder strap drop.
